data.title: Marianna, Florida Population 2024
data.text:
Poverty in Marianna

The race most likely to be in poverty in Marianna is Native , with 100% below the poverty level.

The race least likely to be in poverty in Marianna is White , with 18.1% below the poverty level.

The poverty rate among those that worked full-time for the past 12 months was 2.9% . Among those working part-time, it was 47.23% , and for those that did not work, the poverty rate was 41.56% .
